of
travel
benefits
including
best-in-market
travel
insurance
benefits.
If
you
travel
at
least
a
couple
times
per
year,
this
card
deserves
serious
consideration.
Rewards:
Earn
3
Ultimate
Rewards
points
per
dollar
spent
on
travel
and
at
restaurants
and
1
Ultimate
Reward
point
per
